{"tid":198872,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(求教)希臘Santorini同Mykonos 應該點分配好？","createTime":"2017-04-12T19:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T08:08:42.000Z","uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"96dd31f77699ddc9632c7c79fb34a936a2af9ca2","tid":198872,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:53:16.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊會同朋友去希臘<br />\nDay 1 雅典<br />\nDay 2 雅典<br />\nDay 3 早機去Mykonos <br />\nDay 4 Mykonos-Delos-Mykonos<br />\nDay 5 Mykonos -Santorini <br />\nDay...6,7<br />\n最後一日 返雅典<br />\n<br />\n但問題黎啦，<br />\n我睇遊記話Santorini 應該stay 3日兩夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我個frd就話兩日一夜夠哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打可以解答下Santorini 值唔值三日兩夜，個島好似幾細？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n另外，由Mykonos 去delos 係咪一定要報tour，<br />\n我見一search delos全報都係tour，貌似無online船飛賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9972e87daa62b5f36bb67d71903656526efe54","tid":198872,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:59:23.000Z","msg":"Santorini 2日1夜 撞正落雨你就67 如果唔去火山玩唔遊水 都叫岩岩好既<br />\n<br />\n我上次留4日3夜<br />\nOia 值留一晚"},{"pid":"67ec54cc998ee21a09a0b62c4f6ac1d8ba166506","tid":198872,"uid":40255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T20:06:01.000Z","msg":"我上次都係4日3夜<br />\n本身plan左3日2夜發覺唔夠<br />\nLast 一晚住cave house<br />\n正到呢"},{"pid":"df16fe413f0d3c0fe260d3e76303ec20151d227b","tid":198872,"uid":80909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"同咩朋友去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"