qc8bXRSfVPwy6hKk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=03cbed0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://optikahk.blogspot.hk/2015/08/15.html</a></blockquote><br />\n正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed87c368a71783c627e0a40727454981649a362","tid":198872,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>放棄一日雅典啦</blockquote><br />\n個日數唔係死既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但兩晚雅典係真係唔想太churz，<br />\n慢慢睇下貴跡咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雅典2日點會夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊年影左呢張相,俾sony photo hub貼左堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://c2.staticflickr.com/6/5795/25299762999_a8f5197f16_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F6%2F5795%2F25299762999_a8f5197f16_b.jpg&h=eb99a869&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪有座山，俾你行上去影落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c84b06c4e0d98c2fc532f194f136ca2d9cdd30a","tid":198872,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年係mykonos同santorini都stay左一個星期<br />\nmykonos唔太大其實冇咩野睇，有d悶，睇下風車，行下屋仔，去下beach, 三日夠晒<br />\ndelos我當年都係跟local tour去，唔知依家點<br />\nsantorini 我stay一個星期都覺得差唔多，睇日落，去中間個火山島，紅白黑沙灘，去下酒莊飲酒，睇博物館。好relax, 好halala</blockquote><br />\nDelos係必去,希臘最正的兩個聯合國文化遺產之一,另一個係delphi</blockquote><br />\ndelphi正<br />\n仲有天空之城<br />\n當年好多島都冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd4d5086f7f97fad8937a6f83f693d98465e8cc","tid":198872,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年係mykonos同santorini都stay左一個星期<br />\nmykonos唔太大其實冇咩野睇，有d悶，睇下風車，行下屋仔，去下beach, 三日夠晒<br />\ndelos我當年都係跟local tour去，唔知依家點<br />\nsantorini 我stay一個星期都覺得差唔多，睇日落，去中間個火山島，紅白黑沙灘，去下酒莊飲酒，睇博物館。好relax, 好halala</blockquote><br />\nDelos係必去,希臘最正的兩個聯合國文化遺產之一,另一個係delphi</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打既意見，但如果chur d既話<br />\nDay1 Santorini <br />\nDay2 火山島同Santorini <br />\nDay3 Santorini 返Athen ，接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be58ef8b8ea22935bcb5e9c174acfacd02fca8d4","tid":198872,"uid":79675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年係mykonos同santorini都stay左一個星期<br />\nmykonos唔太大其實冇咩野睇，有d悶，睇下風車，行下屋仔，去下beach, 三日夠晒<br />\ndelos我當年都係跟local tour去，唔知依家點<br />\nsantorini 我stay一個星期都覺得差唔多，睇日落，去中間個火山島，紅白黑沙灘，去下酒莊飲酒，睇博物館。好relax, 好halala</blockquote><br />\nDelos係必去,希臘最正的兩個聯合國文化遺產之一,另一個係delphi</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打既意見，但如果chur d既話<br />\nDay1 Santorini <br />\nDay2 火山島同Santorini <br />\nDay3 Santorini 返Athen ，接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMykonos比我感覺舒服/好玩過santorini，santorini太商業同多遊客<br />\n<br />\nMykonos島細，但人相對少，慢慢行慢慢玩幾舒服，商業區好細，一陣就行完，但搵間好景的cafe可坐兩三個鐘，記得飲Frappe，好好飲。有出名天體沙灘，Super Paradise天體沙灘，不過無去到。可三日兩夜义下電<br />\n<br />\nSantorini島其實幾大，Fira去Oia搭巴士都要半個鐘以上，仲要預塞車<br />\n如果唔係租車，等巴士都佔好多時間，景點多又散，三日兩夜都夠(我自己覺得)。Oia等日落早啲去霸位，一個山頭仔好多人等。<br />\n去到要放慢腳步玩，如果唔係好快行完。不過唔好預佢有好多藍頂白屋⋯⋯其實得好少<br />\n<br />\n每人去完觀感都唔同，我會覺得土耳其好玩過希臘好多，可惜而家政局問題，如果唔係想去多次"},{"pid":"24e5ac8184aac139d7352c594e69738ceb9